### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَهُوَ ٱلَّذِى يُحْىِۦ وَيُمِيتُ وَلَهُ ٱخْتِلَـٰفُ ٱلَّيْلِ وَٱلنَّهَارِ ۚ أَفَلَا تَعْقِلُونَ</span>

### English

And He is the One Who gives life and causes death, and to Him belongs the alternation of the day and night. Will you not then understand?